quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Kandi nyuma ye (Habib an Najar) ntitwigeze twohereza ingabo ziturutse mu kirere (zo kurimbura) abantu be, ndetse nta n’ubwo byari ngombwa ko tuzohereza"
  36,29,Ukurimburwa kwabo kwabaye (gukubitwa n’) urusaku rumwe; nuko barazima (barapfa)
  36,30,Mbega akababaro ku bantu! Nta ntumwa yabageragaho ngo babure kuyisuzugura
  36,31,"Ese ntibabona ibisekuru twarimbuye mbere yabo uko bingana? (Ntibabona ko) mu by’ukuri, batagaruka (ngo bongere kubana nabo)"
  36,32,"Kandi rwose, bose bazazanwa imbere yacu"
  36,33,"Kandi ikimenyetso kuri bo ni ubutaka bwapfuye (bwakakaye) dusubiza ubuzima, maze tukabukuramo imyaka bafungura"
  36,34,"Ndetse twanabushyizeho imirima y’imitende ndetse n’imizabibu, tunashyiramo n’imigezi"
  36,35,Kugira ngo bafungure mu musaruro wayo ndetse no mu byo amaboko yabo atakoze. Ese ntibashobora gushimira
  36,36,"Ubutagatifu ni ubw’Uwaremye ibitsina byombi (ikigabo n’ikigore) mu bintu byose bimera mu butaka, muri bo ubwabo (abantu) ndetse no mu byo batazi"
  36,37,Kandi ikimenyetso kuri bo ni ijoro. Turikuraho (umucyo w’) amanywa maze bakaba mu mwijima
  36,38,"Kandi izuba rigendera mu mwanya waryo (ni ikimenyetso kuri bo). Uko ni ukugena k’Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  36,39,"Ndetse n’ukwezi (ni ikimenyetso kuri bo). Twagushyiriyeho ibyiciro kunyuramo, kugeza ubwo kongeye kuba nk’ishami ry’umutende rishaje"
  36,40,Izuba ntirishobora guhurirana n’ukwezi cyangwa ngo ijoro rize mu mwanya w’amanywa. Kandi byose byogoga mu myanya yabyo
  36,41,N’ikindi kimenyetso kuri bo ni uko twatwaye urubyaro rwabo mu bwato (bwa Nuhu) bwikoreye
  36,42,Twanabaremeye ibindi bisa na bwo bagenderaho
  36,43,"Kandi tubishatse twabaroha, maze ntibabone ubatabara cyangwa ngo barokorwe"
  36,44,"Uretse ku bw’impuhwe ziduturutseho, n’ibyishimo by’igihe gito"
  36,45,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimutinye ibiri imbere yanyu (ibihano byo ku isi) n’ibiri inyuma yanyu (ibihano byo ku mperuka), kugira ngo mugirirwe impuhwe (ntibumva)"
  36,46,Kandi nta kimenyetso na kimwe mu bimenyetso bya Nyagasani wabo cyabageragaho ngo babure kugitera umugongo
  36,47,"N’iyo babwiwe bati \"Nimutange mu byo Allah yabahaye, abahakanye babwira abemera bati \"Ese muragira ngo dufungurire uwo Allah yari gufungurira iyo aza kubishaka? Mwe nta handi muri hatari mu buyobe bugaragara"
  36,48,"Baranavuga bati \"Ese iryo sezerano (izuka) rizaba ryari, niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  36,49,Nta kindi bategereje usibye urusaku rumwe (rw’impanda ya mbere) ruzabakubita bahugiye mu mpaka
  36,50,Nuko ntibashobore kugira umurage basiga habe no gusubira mu miryango yabo
  36,51,"Nuko impanda ivuzwe (bwa kabiri), maze bahite basohoka mu mva (zabo) bagana kwa Nyagasani wabo bihuta"
  36,52,"Bavuga bati \"Mbega ishyano tubonye! Ni nde udukanguye akadukura mu buryamo bwacu?\" (Bazabwirwa bati) \"Ibi ni byo Nyirimpuhwe yasezeranyije, kandi intumwa zavuze ukuri"
  36,53,"(Izurwa ryabo) rizaterwa n’urusaku rumwe (rw’impanda), nuko ubwo bahite bazanwa imbere yacu"
  36,54,"(Babwirwe bati) \"Uyu munsi nta muntu n’umwe uri bugire icyo ahuguzwa, kandi nta kindi muri buhemberwe usibye ibyo mwakoraga"
  36,55,"Mu by’ukuri, abazinjira mu ijuru kuri uwo munsi bazaba bahugijwe n’umunezero"
  36,56,"Bo n’abagore babo bazaba bari mu gicucu, bicaye begamye mu ntebe nziza"
  36,57,Bazarihererwamo imbuto (z’ubwoko bwose) ndetse banabonemo ibyo bifuza byose
  36,58,"(Bazabwirwa bati) \"Salamu\" (mugire amahoro)! Ijambo riturutse kwa Nyagasani, Nyirimbabazi"
  36,59,"Inkozi z’ibibi (zizabwirwa ziti) \"Uyu munsi nimwitandukanye (n’abemeramana)"